    "Nevertheless, it is important to note that the study's restricted sample size, limited age range and cultural impacts impose limitations on the generalizability of the results.",
    "Overall, this pilot study provides a foundation for future research exploring the effectiveness of ChatGPT and other chatbots in improving user experiences.",
    "It is encouraging to observe that ChatGPT was not negatively evaluated and can be effectively utilized in generating lengthy questionnaires.",
